# Install App (PWA)

This website supports [Progressive Web App (PWA)](https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Progressive_web_apps). You can install it on supported browsers for a native app-like experience.

## Mobile

- **Safari (iPhone / iPad)**: Tap the **Share** button at the bottom, scroll down, and select **Add to Home Screen**.
- **Chrome (Android)**: Tap the browser's **Menu** button and select **Add to Home screen** or **Install app**.

## PC

- **Chrome / Edge**: Click the **Install** icon in the address bar, or select **Install app** / **Install Echo** from the browser's menu (•••).
- **Safari (Mac)**: Go to the **File** menu at the top menu bar, and select **Add to Dock**.
